## ðŸŽ¯ Objective
Build an interactive and insightful dashboard for business stakeholders that highlights key KPIs and supports decision-making.

## ðŸ“ˆ Dashboard Features
- **KPIs**:
  - Total Sales
  - Total Profit
  - Orders
  - Profit Margin
- **Visualizations**:
  - Sales & Profit Over Time (Line Chart)
  - Sales by Region (Map or Bar Chart)
  - Category & Sub-Category Performance (Stacked Bar)
  - Customer Segment Breakdown (Donut Chart)
- **Interactivity**:
  - Filters/Slicers by Region, Segment, Date
  - Tooltips for additional insights
  - Dynamic KPIs based on selected filters

## ðŸ§© Design Best Practices
- Used cards for key metrics (Total Sales, Profit, Orders).
- Slicers added for Region, Segment, and Date.
- Applied consistent color theme across the dashboard.
- Interactive charts help identify trends and performance.
- Clean layout with visual hierarchy and minimal clutter.

